    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>(S) In nomine domini nostri Iehsu Christi dei eterni, anno ab incarnatione
                        eius millesimo centesimo trigesimo sexto, sextodecimo kal. martii,
                        indictione quartadecima. Manifesti sumus nos <persName>Rogninus</persName>
                        quondam <persName>Sismundi</persName> et <persName>Iulicta</persName> uxor
                        eius quondam <persName>Guarini</persName> quia nos qui supra iugales (…) ubi
                        interfuit notitia <persName key="#Judge">Fralmi</persName>
                        <rs key="#Judge">iudicis</rs> domni imperatoris (…) vendimus et tradimus
                        tibi <persName>Martino</persName> custodi et rectori <orgName
                            key="#Hospitals" ref="#juridical_persons/3206"><rs key="#Hospitals"
                                >ospitalis</rs> sancti Gilii de <placeName ref="#places/3207"
                                key="#Hospitals">Tepascio</placeName></orgName> tres videlicet
                        petias de terris nostris que esse videntur in loco et finibus <placeName
                            ref="#places/3107">Piciorano</placeName>. Prima quarum ortus, tenet unum
                        caput in <rs>via publica</rs>, alterum in terra et media fossa de filio
                            <persName>Benedicti</persName>, latus in terra
                            <persName>Pedonette</persName> quondam <persName>Lanfranchi</persName>,
                        alterum in terra et media fossa <persName>Guilicionis</persName> quondam
                            <persName>Lanberti</persName>. Secunda dicitur Colognora, caput in terra
                            <persName>Ughi</persName> quondam <persName>Angli</persName>, alterum in
                        terra de <persName>Casalesi</persName>, latus in terra
                            <persName>Tualli</persName>, alterum in terra (…) filii quondam
                            <persName>Lamberti</persName>. Tertia caput in terra et media fossa
                        Tualli, alterum in terra et media fossa <persName>Sifredi</persName>, latus
                        in terra <persName>Ramundini</persName>, alterum in via publica. (…) Pro
                        quibus recepimus pro te meritum aureum a <persName>Guilielmo</persName> pro
                        solidi quinquecentum quinquaginta. (…) <foreign>Pena</foreign>: in duplum.
                        (…) Actum <placeName>Luca</placeName>. (…) Fralmus domni imperatoris iudex
                        interfui et subscripsi. Signum manus <persName>Thabadini</persName> quondam
                            <persName>Ruberti</persName>, <persName>Asini</persName> et
                            <persName>Guidi</persName> germanorum quondam
                        <persName>Guidi</persName>, <persName>Antelmini</persName> quondam
                            <persName>Ughi</persName>, <persName>Sifredi</persName> (…),
                            <persName>Bernardi</persName> quondam <persName>Bernardi</persName>
                        rogatorum trestium (sic). (S) <persName>Guinisius</persName> notarius domni
                        imperatoris post traditam complevi et dedi.</ab>
